#: ../../project_and_asset_management/capturing_audio.rst:20
msgid "Capturing Audio"
msgstr "Captura de audio"

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/capturing_audio.rst:22
msgid ""
"You can use Kdenlive to capture audio with a microphone while you are "
"playing your project in the :doc:`project monitor</user_interface/monitors/"
"project_monitor>`. This way you can record a voiceover. For more details see "
"the chapter :ref:`audio-recording`"
msgstr ""
"Será posible utilizar Kdenlive para capturar audio usando un micrófono, "
"mientras se reproduce el proyecto en el :doc:`Monitor de secuencias </"
"user_interface/monitors/project_monitor>`. De esta forma será posible grabar "
"una locución. Para más detalles, ver la sección :ref:`audio-recording`"

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/capturing_audio.rst:24
msgid ""
"You configure audio capturing from :menuselection:`Menu --> Settings --> "
"Configure Kdenlive -->` :doc:`Capture</getting_started/configure_kdenlive/"
"configuration_capture>`."
msgstr ""
"La grabación de audio podrá ser configurada desde el menú :menuselection:"
"`Preferencias --> Configurar Kdenlive -->` :doc:`Captura </getting_started/"
"configure_kdenlive/configuration_capture>`."

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/capturing_audio.rst:26
msgid ""
"You define the destination location for your captures by using :"
"menuselection:`Menu --> Settings --> Configure Kdenlive --> Environment --"
">` :ref:`Default Folders<configure_environment_default_folders>`."
msgstr ""
"Será posible establecer la ubicación de destino de las grabaciones, mediante "
"el menú :menuselection:`Preferencias --> Configurar Kdenlive --> Entorno --"
">` :ref:`Carpetas predeterminadas <configure_environment_default_folders>`."

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/capturing_audio.rst:37
msgid "Recording a voiceover"
msgstr "Grabando una locución"

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/capturing_audio.rst:39
msgid ""
"The recording will be placed in the timeline where the playhead was when you "
"started the recording."
msgstr ""
"Una vez finalizada, la grabación quedará ubicada a partir de la posición que "
"tenía el cursor de tiempo en el momento de comenzar a grabar."

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/capturing_audio.rst:45
msgid ""
"Depending on your recording device, this may record stereo audio. You can "
"mix it down to mono using the Audio effect :doc:`/effects_and_filters/"
"audio_effects/channels/copy_channels_to_stereo`."
msgstr ""
"Dependiendo del dispositivo de grabación usado, la grabación podría llegar a "
"producir un audio estéreo. Será posible mezclarla a un canal mono usando el "
"efecto de audio :doc:`/effects_and_filters/audio_effects/channels/"
"copy_channels_to_stereo`."

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/capturing_audio.rst:52
msgid ""
"By default, the :file:`.wav` file of the recording is put into the main "
"project bin. If you want your recordings in one place, you can designate a :"
"doc:`folder</project_and_asset_management/project_bin/"
"project_bin_use_folders>` in the project bin as the target for the "
"recordings."
msgstr ""
"De forma predeterminada, el archivo :file:`.wav` producto de una grabación "
"será colocado en el panel de Medios. En caso de que se desearan colocar "
"todas las grabaciones en un mismo lugar, será posible designar a una :doc:"
"`carpeta </project_and_asset_management/project_bin/"
"project_bin_use_folders>` del panel de Medios como la *Carpeta "
"predeterminada para capturas de audio*."

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/capturing_audio.rst:59
msgid "Designating a folder in the bin for audio recordings"
msgstr "Designando a una carpeta como predeterminada para capturas de audio"

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/capturing_audio.rst:61
msgid ""
"Right-click the respective folder in the project bin and enable :guilabel:"
"`Default Target Folder for Audio Captures`."
msgstr ""
"Hacer clic derecho en la carpeta deseada del panel de Medios y seleccionar "
"la opción :guilabel:`Carpeta predeterminada para capturas de audio`."

#: ../../project_and_asset_management/capturing_audio.rst:67
msgid ""
"This folder is a folder in the project bin and not a folder in your file "
"system. You can, however, define a folder in your file system where all "
"recordings (video and audio) are stored. Go to :menuselection:`Menu --> "
"Settings --> Configure Kdenlive --> Environment --> Default Folders`. For "
"more details refer to the chapter :doc:`Settings</getting_started/"
"configuration>`."
msgstr ""
"Se trata de una carpeta virtual del panel de Medios y no de una carpeta real "
"en el sistema de archivos. Es posible, sin embargo, establecer una carpeta "
"en el sistema de archivos para recibir todas las grabaciones (tanto de audio "
"como de video). Ir al menú :menuselection:`Preferencias --> Configurar "
"Kdenlive --> Entorno --> Carpetas predeterminadas`. Para más detalles, "
"consultar la sección :doc:`Configuración </getting_started/configuration>`."

